cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper presents a method for improving the quality of classification of objects based on a combination of known and unknown features. The method is based on a modernized Informational Neurobayesian Approach and was trained on text queries. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
